00:36:58,808 --> 00:37:01,981
[Saijo] Loosening the policies
will force them into dire straits.

531
00:37:02,941 --> 00:37:07,325
It will take away our true national power.

532
00:37:07,826 --> 00:37:09,830
[politicians clamoring]
Exactly. Well said.

533
00:37:09,914 --> 00:37:12,503
It is extremely risky

534
00:37:13,253 --> 00:37:18,138
to pass this bill
without properly debating these issues.

535
00:37:18,222 --> 00:37:20,519
-[politicians] Yes. Exactly.
-[applause]

536
00:37:20,602 --> 00:37:21,688
That's right.

537
00:37:22,271 --> 00:37:23,482
I agree.

538
00:37:25,737 --> 00:37:27,533
-[audience cheers and applauds]
-[music plays]

539
00:37:27,616 --> 00:37:29,035
[fan] Masa!

540
00:37:30,329 --> 00:37:32,375
We've been waiting for you!

541
00:37:34,045 --> 00:37:36,676
-[fan 2] Amazing!
-[fan] You're so cool!

542
00:37:40,057 --> 00:37:43,439
[singing "Season in the Sun"]

543
00:37:43,523 --> 00:37:44,817
Boss!

544
00:37:54,754 --> 00:37:55,756
Yeah!

545
00:37:59,429 --> 00:38:00,932
Boss!

546
00:38:07,946 --> 00:38:11,328
Kiss! Kiss! Kiss!

547
00:38:11,411 --> 00:38:12,581
[music stops]

548
00:38:12,664 --> 00:38:14,668
-Keep singing, Masa!
-[music resumes]

549
00:38:20,806 --> 00:38:21,808
[huffs]

550
00:38:38,591 --> 00:38:41,806
Let's have another toast.

551
00:38:41,889 --> 00:38:44,435
To the upcoming election.

552
00:38:44,520 --> 00:38:47,441
[together] Cheers!

553
00:38:49,028 --> 00:38:50,991
[karaoke playing inside]

554
00:39:05,937 --> 00:39:09,027
We're the police!
Everybody stay where you are!

555
00:39:09,110 --> 00:39:11,574
Don't touch anything! Don't move!

556
00:39:11,657 --> 00:39:13,410
I said don't move!

557
00:39:13,912 --> 00:39:15,039
Get it together!

558
00:39:16,626 --> 00:39:17,920
Nobody touch anything.

559
00:39:18,003 --> 00:39:20,842
Right. Exactly.

560
00:39:20,926 --> 00:39:23,430
-[phone buzzes]
-Oh, sorry. Excuse me.

561
00:39:23,514 --> 00:39:24,516
Thanks.

562
00:39:29,735 --> 00:39:30,737
What's wrong?

563
00:39:31,237 --> 00:39:35,496
[caller] <i>I just received word
your brother has been arrested.</i>

564
00:39:36,791 --> 00:39:39,630
[policeman] Nobody touch anything.
Don't even move!

565
00:39:43,220 --> 00:39:46,226
[caller] <i>Seems he was having a party
at a karaoke bar.</i>

566
00:41:05,635 --> 00:41:07,639
Translated by Annie Chen

